# Patchnotes

## 0.0.7.1

* Fix a crash on the first week of a new game.

## 0.0.7

* Recoloured modules' icons to be more fitting the game's pallet.
* Small adjustments into deep space repair bay activation logic
* [Experimenmtal] Refueling Module - allows refueling ships in deep space.
  Currently has a quirk that depleting refueling tank doesn't lower the total
  mass of the ship (mass calculations in the game are messy).

## 0.0.6

* Fixed a small bug with deep space repairs where it would not execute if
  faction resources dropped a lot prior to the completion.
* Fixed Deep Space Repair becoming unavailable next to a hab without ship
  construction capabilities
* Added fuel refunds on refit completion.
* Added displaying support gain into post combat screen.
* Otherwise mostly internal changes without visible effect

## 0.0.5

* Fixed operations from special modules lingering during transfer.
* Fixed confirmation button for `Clear Debris` not getting active sometimes.
* Added dedicated pre-requisite project for special modules.
* Fixed experience calculation for battles without player faction.
* Added faction support gain upon wins. Alien wins boost protectorate and
  servants.

## 0.0.4

* Display inactive icon for the repair bay if there is no ships with essential
  damage in the fleet
* Fixed crash when fitting engines to utility ship
* Display rank to the list of docked ships
* Fixed missing highlighted deep space repair icon
* Added Debris Cleaner Module
* Added notification screen on deep space repairs finished and debris
  cleaned.
* Made Spacedock tech to be a pre-requisite for building utility ships,
  not warship tech.

## 0.0.3

* Fixed problem with experience being reset over a refit.

## 0.0.2

* Making the mod a collection of various extra's for space ships, not only exp.
* * Saves from the previous release are compatible with the new release.
* New "Utility ship" hull layout.
* Added 'Deep Space Reapir Bay' to allow engine and power plant repairs for
  ships afar from the stations.

## 0.0.1

* Initial cosmetic release
